window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>A healer and a dragon queen. They're meant for each other - and for so much more. </p> <p>A baby, abandoned on a harsh slope to die. She grew into a healer, but she can't grow out of the thing that keeps her from being entirely human. </p> <p>An ice-blue dragon who will one day be queen. Self-confident, and beloved, but there has always been a hole inside her that nothing can fill. </p> <p>Neither of them is ready for what awaits - but the Star doesn't wait for those it calls to be ready.</p>"; 
